                            <comment id="15220088" author="tilman" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2016 15:59:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We can&apos;t support it, because we don&apos;t do the compression ourselves, CCITTFactory just takes the stream from the file. The PDF specification doesn&apos;t support fillorder 2. So the bug is that we don&apos;t refuse such files, I&apos;ll add that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
