&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3299&quot; title=&quot;TIFF-files with FillOrder=2 can&amp;#39;t be converted to PDF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3299&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3299&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: TIFF-files with FillOrder=2 can&apos;t be converted to PDF&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15220266" author="tilman" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2016 17:24:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the detailed report. I&apos;m sorry that the result is just a &quot;you can&apos;t do that&quot; fix. If you need any help re: tiff files / ccitt compression of b/w images, please ask on the mailing list and I&apos;ll be glad to help.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15221306" author="buxxi" created="Fri, 1 Apr 2016 07:29:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok, thanks for the quick reply. At least next time debugging this error wont be so hard &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll find another way to convert these since all of them are really old.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15346727" author="tilman" created="Thu, 23 Jun 2016 16:44:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve just added CCITT encoding from images, see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3069&quot; title=&quot;Add code for CCITT compression&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3069&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3069&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16759523" author="antariksh" created="Sun, 3 Feb 2019 20:35:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=buxxi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;buxxi&quot;&gt;buxxi&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt;: Was there finally any solution to converting tiff files with fill order 2 to its corresponding pdf?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16759530" author="tilman" created="Sun, 3 Feb 2019 20:43:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not directly, for the reason explained in my first comment. What you can do is to read it into a BufferedImage, and then use the CCITTFactory from that one, that will get you a nicely CCITT compressed image (useful if you want very small files) but will take longer.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
